text: Méline Pierret (born 18 January 1999) is a Swiss volleyball player. She is a member of the Women's National Team. She participated at the 2018 Montreux Volley Masters. She plays for TS Volley Düdingen Power Cats. == References == == External links == *FIVB Profile * * *Melissa interviews Swiss Setter, Meline Pierret!
